targets.expr:
sum(

max(kube_pod_labels{label_tier="dundergitcall",label_owner_id=~"$owner_id",label_group_id=~"$group_id",label_service_id=~"$service_id"})
by (label_tier, pod)*on(pod)group_right(label_tier)
label_replace
(sum by(pod,container)
(
rate(container_cpu_usage_seconds_total{container=~".*",container!="POD",container!="",image!=""}[2m])
), "pod", "$1", "pod_name", "(.+)")

) 

/

sum(

max(kube_pod_labels{label_tier="dundergitcall",label_owner_id=~"$owner_id",label_group_id=~"$group_id",label_service_id=~"$service_id"})
by (label_tier, pod)*on(pod)group_right(label_tier)
label_replace
(

(kube_pod_container_resource_limits_cpu_cores{}

), "pod", "$1", "pod", "(.+)")

)

* 100

sum(kube_pod_status_phase{phase="Running"} * on(pod) group_left() max(kube_pod_labels{label_tier="dundergitcall",label_owner_id=~"$owner_id",label_group_id=~"$group_id",label_service_id=~"$service_id"}) by (label_tier, label_owner_id, label_group_id, label_service_id, pod))

sum(kube_pod_status_phase{phase="Pending"} * on(pod) group_left() max(kube_pod_labels{label_tier="dundergitcall",label_owner_id=~"$owner_id",label_group_id=~"$group_id",label_service_id=~"$service_id"}) by (label_tier, label_owner_id, label_group_id, label_service_id, pod))

sum(kube_pod_status_phase{phase="Failed"} * on(pod) group_left() max(kube_pod_labels{label_tier="dundergitcall",label_owner_id=~"$owner_id",label_group_id=~"$group_id",label_service_id=~"$service_id"}) by (label_tier, label_owner_id, label_group_id, label_service_id, pod))
